::Choo Bee::Corporate Info - Fact Sheet


















































































 Manufacturing
                    Division


  Contributes
                      approximately 40% of the Group’s Turnover 



  Our main manufacturing plant is in Pengkalan at Lahat, Ipoh             
 with land area of 30 acres and   installed capacity of machineries            
 of approximately 370,000 metric tonnes per annum



  Our pipes and tubes production processes use Electric Resistance Welding (ERW) technology  from Japan and Taiwan.



  Our Quality Management System (ISO 9001 : 2015) is certified by Intertek Certification  International Sdn. Bhd. Our other product certifications are from American Petroleum Institute   (API), TUV Rheinland Malaysia Sdn. Bhd. and IKRAM QA Services Sdn. Bhd. 







 Pengkalan
                      Plant



Lot 65580, Kawasan Perusahaan Pengkalan 1, 31500 Lahat, Perak 








 Menglembu
                      Plant



                No. 9, Hala Perusahaan Menglembu 1, Kawasan Perusahaan Menglembu, 30200 Ipoh, Perak


