Stock Exchange Listing

 Main Board of Bursa Malaysia Securities Berhad




Stock Code

 5797 (Industrial Product)




Date of Listing 

 12 October 1994




Share Capital 

 109,903,000 ordinary shares of RM 1 each

 


Principal Activities 

 Manufacturing of steel products mainly for oil and gas application, building and construction industries, trading of hardware products such as   
 beams, channels, mild steel plates, flat bars, angle bars, stainless steel 
 products and other building materials as well as provision of steel  
 servicing such as slitting and shearing of coils




Main Products 

 API 5L Line Pipes, Cement Lined Pipes, Circular, Square and Rectangular Hollow Sections, Furniture Tubes and Lipped Channels




 
 


 



