                                                Choo Bee Metal Industries Berhad
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Choo Bee Metal Industries Berhad operates within the Steel pipe and tubes sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Choo Bee Metal Industries Berhad with three other
	steel companies in Asia:
		
	Samchai Steel Industries Public Company Limited
	
		of Thailand
		(2016
	sales of 2.86 billion Thai Bahts [US$85.93  million]
		),
	
	India Steel Works Limited
	
		of India
		(5.84 billion Indian Rupees [US$90.97  million]
		), and
	
	Ruchi Strips And Alloys Limited
	
		which is
		
			also
		
		based in India
		(4.75 billion Indian Rupees [US$74.01  million]
		).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	
		During the year ended December of 2016, sales at
		Choo Bee Metal Industries Berhad were 369.63 million Malaysian Ringgits (US$86.32 million).
	
		This
		
			is
		
			a
			
			decrease of 19.9%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 461.21 million Malaysian Ringgits.
	
		Contributing to the drop in overall sales was the 25.0% decline
		in Manufacturing, from 179.96 million Malaysian Ringgits to 134.90 million Malaysian Ringgits.
		
					There were also decreases in sales in
					Trading (down 16.5% to 234.72 million Malaysian Ringgits)
				.
		

	





 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










