Choo Bee Metal Industries Bhd Company Profile

 
			

Get an in-depth profile of Choo Bee Metal Industries Bhd, including a general overview of the company's business and key management, as well as employee data and location and contact information.









 


IndustryConstr. - Supplies & Fixtures
SectorCapital Goods
Employees246
Equity TypeORD


Choo Bee Metal Industries Berhad is engaged in the processing of steel coils into steel products, fabrication of steel products and trading of hardware products. The Company operates through two segments: Trading and Manufacturing. The Trading segment deals in hardware and construction materials. The Manufacturing segment is engaged in the processing of steel coils into steel products and fabrication of steel products. The Company manufactures steel products for oil and gas application, building and construction industries, trading of hardware products, such as beams, channels, mild steel plates, flat bars, angle bars, stainless steel products and other building materials, as well as provision of steel servicing, such as slitting and shearing of coils. It offers various products, such as Welded Steel Pipe & Galvanized Iron Pipe, Carbon Steel Pipe for Ordinary Piping, Carbon Steel Tube for Machine Structural Purpose, Window Pipe, Galvanized Steel Conduit Pipe and Decor & String Pipe.


Contact Information


Address
Ipoh, 31650Malaysia



Phone
+60-5-2558111



Fax
5-2543073



Web
www.choobee.com.my




