Company Description                    




                        Choo Bee Metal Industries Berhad is engaged in the processing of steel coils into steel products, fabrication of steel products and trading of hardware products. Choo Bee Metal's products include welded steel pipes and galvanized iron pipes, carbon steel pipes for ordinary piping, carbon steel tubes for machine structural purpose, window pipe, galvanized steel conduit pipes, and decor and string pipes. Choo Bee Metal was founded in 1971 and based in Petaling Jaya, Selangor, Malaysia. The company is listed on Bursa Malaysia under the Main Market.                     


